Package com.intel.icecp.rpc

  • Interface Summary 
    Interface Description
    OnCommandMessage<M extends Module,T>
    Interface used to process commands received by the module
    RpcClient  
    RpcServer
    Created by nmgaston on 5/20/2016.
  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    Command
    Represent a command that can be executed by both internal or remote agents; presents an addressing pattern (Command.name() for finding and calling methods, especially over the network.
    CommandDescription
    Describes a Command using JSON schemas for inputs and outputs; this object is used for discovering what commands are available and how to call them.
    CommandRegistry
    Manage commands in a central registry, controlling access to the commands using Java permissions.
    CommandRequest
    Represent a request to execute a command Command
    CommandResponse
    Represent a response to a Command invocation
    Rpc
